    <formalpara>
      <title>2009-10-27 Testing BibleTime for Windows</title>

      <para>We are pleased to announce that BibleTime is now ready
	for testing on your 
	<ulink url="http://devel.bibletime.info/wiki/Release_announcements#2009-10-27_Windows_installer_available_for_testing">Windows PC</ulink>.</para>

	<title>BibleTime 2.3.3 bugfix released</title>

	<para>BT 2.3.3 bugfix has been released.  All packagers and maintainers
